Guidelines Welcome to Ringtone Tutorial! The Ringtone Maker app is designed to simplify the process of creating and customizing ringtones to your liking. Here are some important guidelines: Create ringtones from existing tracks: Select the track you want to convert into a ringtone, then specify the area to cut and customize as desired. Lofi Sound 120 Sound Rock Sound Ballad Dreamers Cut and edit audio: Use cutting tools, adjust volume, and add effects to create unique sound sequences. Store: Once created, you can store your ringtones on your device or in tab My Sounds for later use. Support and assistance: If you encounter any problems or have questions, please see help or contact us for assistance. Thank you for using Ringtone Maker and hope you have a great experience creating your own unique ringtones! Best of 2023
